{"id":10648,"date":"2024-01-12T12:51:09","date_gmt":"2024-01-12T05:51:09","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/?p=10648"},"modified":"2024-01-12T12:52:44","modified_gmt":"2024-01-12T05:52:44","slug":"mua-nha-chung-cu-co-duoc-cap-so-do-khong","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/mua-nha-chung-cu-co-duoc-cap-so-do-khong\/","title":{"rendered":"Mua nh\u00e0 chung c\u01b0 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea5p s\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ecf kh\u00f4ng?"},"content":{"rendered":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Khi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh mua chung c\u01b0, vi\u1ec7c c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ecf l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 quan tr\u1ecdng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1ecf qua. S\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ecf kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ee9ng minh quy\u1ec1n s\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u00e0 c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o t\u00ednh ph\u00e1p l\u00fd v\u00e0 an to\u00e0n giao d\u1ecbch. Ng\u00e0y nay, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm c\u00e1c c\u0103n h\u1ed9 th\u01b0\u1eddng th\u1eafc m\u1eafc <\/span>mua nh\u00e0 chung c\u01b0 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea5p s\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ecf kh\u00f4ng<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">? H\u00e3y c\u00f9ng <\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><strong>Vinhomeland<\/strong><\/a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> \u0111i t\u00ecm c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi cho c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi n\u00e0y nh\u00e9!<\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">S\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ecf v\u00e0 s\u1ed5 h\u1ed3ng kh\u00e1c nhau nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o?<\/span><\/strong><\/h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Tr\u00ean th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, vi\u1ec7c g\u1ecdi &#8220;s\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ecf&#8221; v\u00e0 &#8220;s\u1ed5 h\u1ed3ng&#8221; ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch m\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ec3 mi\u00eau t\u1ea3 Gi\u1ea5y ch\u1ee9ng nh\u1eadn s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ea5t, v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t gi\u1eefa ch\u00fang ch\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t t\u1eeb c\u01a1 quan c\u1ea5p s\u1ed5. <\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">S\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ecf, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Ban h\u00e0nh b\u1edfi B\u1ed9 T\u00e0i nguy\u00ean v\u00e0 M\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng, l\u00e0 n\u01a1i ghi ch\u00fa r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng v\u1ec1 quy\u1ec1n s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ea5t, bao g\u1ed3m c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ea5t nh\u00e0 \u1edf, \u0111\u1ea5t s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t, \u0111\u1ea5t ao, v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea5t v\u01b0\u1eddn. Trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh n\u00e0y, gi\u1ea5y ch\u1ee9ng nh\u1eadn quy\u1ec1n s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c coi l\u00e0 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 quy\u1ec1n v\u00e0 l\u1ee3i \u00edch h\u1ee3p ph\u00e1p c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ea5t, theo quy \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a Lu\u1eadt \u0111\u1ea5t \u0111ai n\u0103m 2003.<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, s\u1ed5 h\u1ed3ng, v\u1edbi m\u00e0u s\u1eafc h\u1ed3ng n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea5p b\u1edfi B\u1ed9 X\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng v\u00e0 ghi ch\u00e9p th\u00f4ng tin li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn quy\u1ec1n s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u00e0 \u1edf v\u00e0 quy\u1ec1n s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ea5t \u1edf, theo quy \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a \u0110i\u1ec1u 11 c\u1ee7a Lu\u1eadt nh\u00e0 \u1edf n\u0103m 2005. C\u00f3 hai tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p ch\u00ednh khi ng\u01b0\u1eddi mua nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea5p s\u1ed5 h\u1ed3ng: khi h\u1ecd l\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u00f9ng l\u00fac c\u1ee7a c\u1ea3 nh\u00e0 \u1edf v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea5t \u1edf, v\u00e0 khi h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u00e0 \u1edf m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng s\u1edf h\u1eefu \u0111\u1ea5t.<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">T\u1eeb th\u00e1ng 10\/2009 tr\u1edf \u0111i, c\u01a1 quan c\u1ea5p s\u1ed5 \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n vi\u1ec7c cung c\u1ea5p m\u1ed9t m\u1eabu gi\u1ea5y ch\u1ee9ng nh\u1eadn m\u1edbi mang t\u00ean &#8220;Gi\u1ea5y ch\u1ee9ng nh\u1eadn quy\u1ec1n s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ea5t, quy\u1ec1n s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u00e0 \u1edf v\u00e0 t\u00e0i s\u1ea3n kh\u00e1c g\u1eafn li\u1ec1n v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea5t,&#8221; \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ea5t v\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u00e0 \u1edf, bao g\u1ed3m c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng t\u00e0i s\u1ea3n kh\u00e1c k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea5t.<\/span><\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_10650\" style=\"width: 810px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-10650\" class=\"wp-image-10650 size-full lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/mua-nha-chung-cu-co-duoc-cap-so-do-khong-1.jpg\" alt=\"mua nh\u00e0 chung c\u01b0 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea5p s\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ecf kh\u00f4ng\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 800px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 800\/450;\" \/><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-10650\" class=\"wp-image-10650 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/mua-nha-chung-cu-co-duoc-cap-so-do-khong-1.jpg\" alt=\"mua nh\u00e0 chung c\u01b0 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea5p s\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ecf kh\u00f4ng\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" \/><\/noscript><p id=\"caption-attachment-10650\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Nh\u1eefng kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t gi\u1eefa s\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ecf v\u00e0 s\u1ed5 h\u1ed3ng ch\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t t\u1eeb c\u01a1 quan c\u1ea5p s\u1ed5.<\/p><\/div>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Mua chung c\u01b0 c\u00f3 s\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ecf kh\u00f4ng?<\/span><\/strong><\/h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Theo quy \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a Lu\u1eadt nh\u00e0 \u1edf n\u0103m 2014, nh\u1eefng c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u00e0 \u1edf h\u1ee3p ph\u00e1p v\u00e0 k\u00fd k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng mua b\u00e1n theo \u0111\u00fang quy \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea5p Gi\u1ea5y ch\u1ee9ng nh\u1eadn quy\u1ec1n s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ea5t v\u00e0 Quy\u1ec1n s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u00e0 \u1edf, c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi t\u00e0i s\u1ea3n g\u1eafn li\u1ec1n v\u1edbi m\u1ea3nh \u0111\u1ea5t n\u00e0y. T\u00e0i li\u1ec7u n\u00e0y th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi l\u00e0 Gi\u1ea5y ch\u1ee9ng nh\u1eadn nh\u00e0 \u1edf v\u00e0 c\u00f3 m\u00e0u h\u1ed3ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Do \u0111\u00f3, khi mua chung c\u01b0, ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 nh\u00e0 \u1edf \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1eb5n, ch\u1ee7 s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u1ee7a c\u0103n h\u1ed9 s\u1ebd nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Gi\u1ea5y ch\u1ee9ng nh\u1eadn quy\u1ec1n s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ea5t, k\u00e8m theo quy\u1ec1n s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u00e0 \u1edf v\u00e0 t\u00e0i s\u1ea3n li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5t.<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Nh\u1eefng quy\u1ec1n c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi mua nh\u00e0 chung c\u01b0 v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea5p s\u1ed5 h\u1ed3ng bao g\u1ed3m:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Quy\u1ec1n s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u0103n h\u1ed9 chung c\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 mua.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Quy\u1ec1n s\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n khu \u0111\u1ea5t d\u00e0nh cho x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng nh\u00e0 chung c\u01b0.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u1ee7a c\u0103n h\u1ed9 chung c\u01b0 ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng khu \u0111\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 t\u00f2a nh\u00e0 chung c\u01b0 m\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi mua thu\u1ed9c. N\u1ebfu ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 chung c\u01b0 thu\u00ea \u0111\u1ea5t t\u1eeb nh\u00e0 n\u01b0\u1edbc v\u1edbi th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 50 n\u0103m, th\u00ec s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u0103n h\u1ed9 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c duy tr\u00ec trong kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u00f3. Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p gi\u1ea5y ch\u1ee9ng nh\u1eadn quy\u1ec1n s\u1edf h\u1eefu \u0111\u1ea5t x\u00e2y t\u00f2a nh\u00e0 l\u00e0 l\u00e2u d\u00e0i ho\u1eb7c v\u0129nh vi\u1ec5n, th\u00ec th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u1ee7a c\u0103n h\u1ed9 chung c\u01b0 c\u0169ng s\u1ebd l\u00e0 l\u00e2u d\u00e0i.<\/span><\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_10651\" style=\"width: 810px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-10651\" class=\"wp-image-10651 size-full lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/mua-nha-chung-cu-co-duoc-cap-so-do-khong-2.jpg\" alt=\"mua nh\u00e0 chung c\u01b0 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea5p s\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ecf kh\u00f4ng\" width=\"800\" height=\"626\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 800px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 800\/626;\" \/><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-10651\" class=\"wp-image-10651 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/mua-nha-chung-cu-co-duoc-cap-so-do-khong-2.jpg\" alt=\"mua nh\u00e0 chung c\u01b0 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea5p s\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ecf kh\u00f4ng\" width=\"800\" height=\"626\" \/><\/noscript><p id=\"caption-attachment-10651\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Khi mua chung c\u01b0, ch\u1ee7 s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u1ee7a c\u0103n h\u1ed9 s\u1ebd nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Gi\u1ea5y ch\u1ee9ng nh\u1eadn quy\u1ec1n s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ea5t<\/p><\/div>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Th\u1eddi gian c\u1ea5p s\u1ed5 h\u1ed3ng cho c\u0103n h\u1ed9 l\u00e0 bao l\u00e2u?<\/span><\/strong><\/h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">D\u1ef1 \u00e1n chung c\u01b0, khi ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng theo \u0111\u00fang quy \u0111\u1ecbnh, t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n cho vi\u1ec7c mua b\u00e1n v\u1edbi kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng tr\u1edf n\u00ean h\u1ee3p ph\u00e1p. Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng mua nh\u00e0 v\u00e0 thanh to\u00e1n \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea5p Gi\u1ea5y ch\u1ee9ng nh\u1eadn quy\u1ec1n s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u00e0 \u1edf.<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Sau \u0111\u00f3, b\u00ean b\u00e1n s\u1ebd ch\u1ecbu tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t c\u00e1c th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec3 c\u01a1 quan nh\u00e0 n\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00f3 th\u1ea9m quy\u1ec1n c\u1ea5p Gi\u1ea5y ch\u1ee9ng nh\u1eadn quy\u1ec1n s\u1edf h\u1eefu cho b\u00ean mua c\u0103n h\u1ed9 chung c\u01b0. \u0110\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi, ng\u01b0\u1eddi mua c\u1ea7n chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb h\u1ed3 s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ec1 xu\u1ea5t c\u1ea5p Gi\u1ea5y ch\u1ee9ng nh\u1eadn quy\u1ec1n s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u00e0 \u1edf l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u khi mua c\u0103n h\u1ed9 trong d\u1ef1 \u00e1n \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, theo \u0111i\u1ec1u 13 c\u1ee7a Lu\u1eadt Kinh doanh B\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u1ea3n n\u0103m 2014, quy \u0111\u1ecbnh nh\u01b0 sau: &#8220;Trong th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 50 ng\u00e0y k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y b\u00e0n giao nh\u00e0 ho\u1eb7c k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y h\u1ebft h\u1ea1n thu\u00ea mua, b\u00ean b\u00e1n ph\u1ea3i th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec3 c\u01a1 quan nh\u00e0 n\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00f3 th\u1ea9m quy\u1ec1n c\u1ea5p Gi\u1ea5y ch\u1ee9ng nh\u1eadn quy\u1ec1n s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ea5t, quy\u1ec1n s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u00e0 \u1edf v\u00e0 c\u00e1c t\u00e0i s\u1ea3n kh\u00e1c li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5t cho b\u00ean mua, b\u00ean thu\u00ea mua. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y tr\u1eeb khi c\u00f3 v\u0103n b\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u1ee7a b\u00ean mua, b\u00ean thu\u00ea mua y\u00eau c\u1ea7u t\u1ef1 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c c\u1ea5p Gi\u1ea5y ch\u1ee9ng nh\u1eadn.&#8221;<\/span><\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_10652\" style=\"width: 810px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-10652\" class=\"wp-image-10652 size-full lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/mua-nha-chung-cu-co-duoc-cap-so-do-khong-3.jpg\" alt=\"mua nh\u00e0 chung c\u01b0 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea5p s\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ecf kh\u00f4ng\" width=\"800\" height=\"469\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 800px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 800\/469;\" \/><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-10652\" class=\"wp-image-10652 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/mua-nha-chung-cu-co-duoc-cap-so-do-khong-3.jpg\" alt=\"mua nh\u00e0 chung c\u01b0 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea5p s\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ecf kh\u00f4ng\" width=\"800\" height=\"469\" \/><\/noscript><p id=\"caption-attachment-10652\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Th\u1eddi gian c\u1ea5p s\u1ed5 h\u1ed3ng cho c\u0103n h\u1ed9 l\u00e0 trong th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 50 ng\u00e0y<\/p><\/div>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c ph\u00e1p l\u00fd c\u1ea7n n\u1eafm khi mua chung c\u01b0<\/span><\/strong><\/h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e2n c\u1ea7n n\u1eafm v\u1eefng m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 khi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh mua chung c\u01b0, bao g\u1ed3m:<\/span><\/p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Ch\u1ee7 d\u1ef1 \u00e1n c\u1ee7a chung c\u01b0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh mua<\/span><\/strong><\/h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 d\u1ef1 \u00e1n m\u1edbi \u0111ang chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng, m\u1ed9t b\u01b0\u1edbc quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u k\u1ef9 v\u1ec1 ch\u1ee7 d\u1ef1 \u00e1n. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y bao g\u1ed3m vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o r\u1eb1ng ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh m\u00e0 c\u00f2n c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng tri\u1ec3n khai d\u1ef1 \u00e1n m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3. Quan tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n, vi\u1ec7c ki\u1ec3m tra xem ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea5p gi\u1ea5y ph\u00e9p kinh doanh d\u1ef1 \u00e1n h\u1ee3p ph\u00e1p t\u1eeb S\u1edf K\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch l\u00e0 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o r\u1eb1ng d\u1ef1 \u00e1n s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 \u0111\u00ecnh tr\u1ec7 hay b\u1ecb ng\u1eebng thi c\u00f4ng gi\u1eefa ch\u1eebng.<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, v\u1edbi d\u1ef1 \u00e1n chung c\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh, s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eb7t v\u00e0o th\u00f4ng tin li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0. Khi ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 cung c\u1ea5p th\u00f4ng tin minh b\u1ea1ch v\u00e0 r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng v\u1ec1 quy\u1ec1n l\u1ef1c kinh doanh d\u1ef1 \u00e1n, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 vi\u1ec7c x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00f3 hay kh\u00f4ng t\u00e0i s\u1ea3n th\u1ebf ch\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ec3 vay v\u1ed1n, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 quan tr\u1ecdng trong vi\u1ec7c b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi mua kh\u1ecfi r\u1ee7i ro ti\u1ec1m \u1ea9n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng l\u1eeba \u0111\u1ea3o. Vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ec1 cao s\u1ef1 minh b\u1ea1ch n\u00e0y gi\u00fap ng\u01b0\u1eddi mua x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n cho m\u1ed9t giao d\u1ecbch b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u1ea3n an to\u00e0n v\u00e0 minh b\u1ea1ch.<\/span><\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_10653\" style=\"width: 810px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-10653\" class=\"wp-image-10653 size-full lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/mua-nha-chung-cu-co-duoc-cap-so-do-khong-4.jpg\" alt=\"mua nh\u00e0 chung c\u01b0 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea5p s\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ecf kh\u00f4ng\" width=\"800\" height=\"469\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 800px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 800\/469;\" \/><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-10653\" class=\"wp-image-10653 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/mua-nha-chung-cu-co-duoc-cap-so-do-khong-4.jpg\" alt=\"mua nh\u00e0 chung c\u01b0 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea5p s\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ecf kh\u00f4ng\" width=\"800\" height=\"469\" \/><\/noscript><p id=\"caption-attachment-10653\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Ch\u1ee7 d\u1ef1 \u00e1n c\u1ee7a chung c\u01b0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh mua<\/p><\/div>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Gi\u1ea5y ch\u1ee9ng nh\u1eadn quy\u1ec1n s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ea5t<\/span><\/strong><\/h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Gi\u1ea5y ch\u1ee9ng nh\u1eadn quy\u1ec1n s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ea5t, nh\u01b0 s\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ecf ho\u1eb7c quy\u1ec1n thu\u00ea \u0111\u1ea5t, \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 quan tr\u1ecdng trong c\u00e1c d\u1ef1 \u00e1n x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 khi d\u1ef1 \u00e1n \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh v\u00e0 \u0111i v\u00e0o s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng. Nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea5y t\u1edd n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ee9ng nh\u1eadn t\u00ednh h\u1ee3p ph\u00e1p c\u1ee7a d\u1ef1 \u00e1n x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng m\u00e0 c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o r\u1eb1ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u00e1c tranh ch\u1ea5p ph\u00e1p l\u00fd v\u1edbi b\u00ean th\u1ee9 ba.<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t quan tr\u1ecdng, l\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 gi\u1eef c\u00e1c gi\u1ea5y t\u1edd n\u00e0y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch ch\u1ee9ng minh r\u1eb1ng d\u1ef1 \u00e1n kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb th\u1ebf ch\u1ea5p t\u1ea1i ng\u00e2n h\u00e0ng. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y l\u00e0 c\u1ea5p thi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ec3 x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn t\u00ednh minh b\u1ea1ch v\u00e0 an to\u00e0n c\u1ee7a d\u1ef1 \u00e1n, t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n cho vi\u1ec7c qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd v\u00e0 giao d\u1ecbch b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u1ea3n m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd v\u00e0 c\u00f3 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3.<\/span><\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_10654\" style=\"width: 810px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-10654\" class=\"wp-image-10654 size-full lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/mua-nha-chung-cu-co-duoc-cap-so-do-khong-5.jpg\" alt=\"mua nh\u00e0 chung c\u01b0 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea5p s\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ecf kh\u00f4ng\" width=\"800\" height=\"469\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 800px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 800\/469;\" \/><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-10654\" class=\"wp-image-10654 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/mua-nha-chung-cu-co-duoc-cap-so-do-khong-5.jpg\" alt=\"mua nh\u00e0 chung c\u01b0 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea5p s\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ecf kh\u00f4ng\" width=\"800\" height=\"469\" \/><\/noscript><p id=\"caption-attachment-10654\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Gi\u1ea5y ch\u1ee9ng nh\u1eadn quy\u1ec1n s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ea5t, nh\u01b0 s\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ecf, \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 quan tr\u1ecdng trong c\u00e1c d\u1ef1 \u00e1n x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng<\/p><\/div>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Gi\u1ea5y ph\u00e9p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng d\u1ef1 \u00e1n<\/span><\/strong><\/h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Gi\u1ea5y ph\u00e9p x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t d\u1ef1 \u00e1n kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ee9ng minh r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 cho ph\u00e9p t\u1eeb ph\u00eda nh\u00e0 n\u01b0\u1edbc cho vi\u1ec7c x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng, m\u00e0 c\u00f2n kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eb1ng d\u1ef1 \u00e1n \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n theo quy \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 n\u01b0\u1edbc. \u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng d\u1ef1 \u00e1n \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n gi\u1ea5y ph\u00e9p, vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o ti\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9 x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng \u0111\u00fang k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 gi\u1ea3m nguy c\u01a1 b\u1ecb \u0111\u00ecnh ch\u1ec9 thi c\u00f4ng m\u00e0 c\u00f2n t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng nh\u1eadn nh\u00e0 \u0111\u00fang h\u1ea1n cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi mua.<\/span><\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_10655\" style=\"width: 810px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-10655\" class=\"wp-image-10655 size-full lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/mua-nha-chung-cu-co-duoc-cap-so-do-khong-6.jpg\" alt=\"mua nh\u00e0 chung c\u01b0 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea5p s\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ecf kh\u00f4ng\" width=\"800\" height=\"469\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 800px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 800\/469;\" \/><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-10655\" class=\"wp-image-10655 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/mua-nha-chung-cu-co-duoc-cap-so-do-khong-6.jpg\" alt=\"mua nh\u00e0 chung c\u01b0 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea5p s\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ecf kh\u00f4ng\" width=\"800\" height=\"469\" \/><\/noscript><p id=\"caption-attachment-10655\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Gi\u1ea5y ph\u00e9p x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t d\u1ef1 \u00e1n ch\u1ee9ng minh r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 cho ph\u00e9p t\u1eeb ph\u00eda nh\u00e0 n\u01b0\u1edbc cho vi\u1ec7c x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng.<\/p><\/div>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">D\u1ef1 \u00e1n n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 n\u1ed9p ti\u1ec1n s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng v\u00e0 thu\u1ebf \u0111\u1ea5t ch\u01b0a?<\/span><\/strong><\/h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a d\u1ef1 \u00e1n, ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 c\u1ea7n th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 c\u00e1c ngh\u0129a v\u1ee5 t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi nh\u00e0 n\u01b0\u1edbc li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn d\u1ef1 \u00e1n. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y l\u00e0 quan tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi mua c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c l\u00e0m s\u1ed5 h\u1ed3ng cho c\u0103n h\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Do \u0111\u00f3, gi\u1ea5y t\u1edd n\u00e0y tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n quan tr\u1ecdng trong th\u00f4ng tin m\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 c\u1ea7n xu\u1ea5t tr\u00ecnh m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch minh b\u1ea1ch v\u00e0 c\u00f4ng khai cho nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi mua.<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">\u0110\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o an to\u00e0n h\u01a1n, ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e2n n\u00ean li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi c\u01a1 quan S\u1edf X\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng \u0111\u1ec3 x\u00e1c minh th\u00f4ng tin, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi ki\u1ec3m tra xem nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin m\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 cung c\u1ea5p c\u00f3 ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c hay kh\u00f4ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh mua chung c\u01b0 thu\u1ed9c d\u1ef1 \u00e1n \u0111\u00f3.<\/span><\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_10656\" style=\"width: 810px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-10656\" class=\"wp-image-10656 size-full lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/mua-nha-chung-cu-co-duoc-cap-so-do-khong-7.jpg\" alt=\"mua nh\u00e0 chung c\u01b0 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea5p s\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ecf kh\u00f4ng\" width=\"800\" height=\"469\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 800px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 800\/469;\" \/><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-10656\" class=\"wp-image-10656 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/mua-nha-chung-cu-co-duoc-cap-so-do-khong-7.jpg\" alt=\"mua nh\u00e0 chung c\u01b0 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea5p s\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ecf kh\u00f4ng\" width=\"800\" height=\"469\" \/><\/noscript><p id=\"caption-attachment-10656\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">D\u1ef1 \u00e1n n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 n\u1ed9p ti\u1ec1n s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng v\u00e0 thu\u1ebf \u0111\u1ea5t ch\u01b0a?<\/p><\/div>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">H\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng mua b\u00e1n chung c\u01b0<\/span><\/strong><\/h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">M\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea5y t\u1edd quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t, \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m v\u00e0 quy\u1ec1n l\u1ee3i c\u1ee7a c\u1ea3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi mua v\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0, l\u00e0 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng mua chung c\u01b0. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi k\u00fd k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng n\u00e0y, vi\u1ec7c ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 th\u00f4ng tin quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 quan tr\u1ecdng:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">\u0110\u01a1n v\u1ecb ti\u1ec1n trong h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ec9 r\u00f5 l\u00e0 VN\u0110; n\u1ebfu s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb ti\u1ec1n t\u1ec7 kh\u00e1c, trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p tranh ch\u1ea5p, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n khi \u0111\u01b0a ra x\u00e9t x\u1eed t\u1ea1i t\u00f2a \u00e1n.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi k\u00fd t\u00ean tr\u00ean h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 ho\u1eb7c ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c u\u1ef7 quy\u1ec1n h\u1ee3p l\u1ec7 t\u1eeb ph\u00eda ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">C\u00e1c tho\u1ea3 thu\u1eadn v\u1ec1 chi ph\u00ed li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ea5t, bao g\u1ed3m c\u00e1c chi ph\u00ed qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd, v\u1ec7 sinh, b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7, hay gi\u1eef xe, c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u00f4 t\u1ea3 r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng trong h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">\u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c d\u1ef1 \u00e1n \u0111ang trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng, vi\u1ec7c k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i di\u1ec5n ra sau khi ph\u1ea7n m\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a d\u1ef1 \u00e1n \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh. Quy \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u00e0y nh\u1eb1m b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 quy\u1ec1n l\u1ee3i c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi mua v\u00e0 th\u1eddi gian thanh to\u00e1n li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng c\u1ee7a d\u1ef1 \u00e1n.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<div id=\"attachment_10657\" style=\"width: 810px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-10657\" class=\"wp-image-10657 size-full lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/mua-nha-chung-cu-co-duoc-cap-so-do-khong-8.jpg\" alt=\"mua nh\u00e0 chung c\u01b0 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea5p s\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ecf kh\u00f4ng\" width=\"800\" height=\"469\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 800px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 800\/469;\" \/><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-10657\" class=\"wp-image-10657 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/mua-nha-chung-cu-co-duoc-cap-so-do-khong-8.jpg\" alt=\"mua nh\u00e0 chung c\u01b0 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea5p s\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ecf kh\u00f4ng\" width=\"800\" height=\"469\" \/><\/noscript><p id=\"caption-attachment-10657\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">H\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng mua b\u00e1n chung c\u01b0<\/p><\/div>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><b>L\u1eddi k\u1ebft<\/b><\/span><\/h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Vi\u1ec7c x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh li\u1ec7u <\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/mua-nha-chung-cu-co-duoc-cap-so-do-khong\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><strong>mua nh\u00e0 chung c\u01b0 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea5p s\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ecf kh\u00f4ng<\/strong><\/a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec3m tra c\u1ea9n th\u1eadn v\u00e0 hi\u1ec3u bi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 quy tr\u00ecnh ph\u00e1p l\u00fd li\u00ean quan, gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o m\u1ed9t giao d\u1ecbch mua nh\u00e0 chung c\u01b0 an to\u00e0n v\u00e0 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.<\/span><\/span><\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"kk-star-ratings kksr-auto kksr-align-right kksr-valign-bottom\"\n    data-payload='{&quot;align&quot;:&quot;right&quot;,&quot;id&quot;:&quot;10648&quot;,&quot;slug&quot;:&quot;default&quot;,&quot;valign&quot;:&quot;bottom&quot;,&quot;i